data.name: commandLineHelp.Text
data.value:
Program actions, while start
RTSP mosaic VLC player.exe [fullscreen] [screen=N] [autoplay] [unmute] [priority=N]
fullscreen - maximize window screen=N - move window to screen number N (0,1,2,...) autoplay - automatically play positioned cameras unmute - unmute sound, if it exist on start playing priority=N - change program priority, N: 0 - Idle 1 - Below Normal 2 - Normal 3 - Above Normal 4 - High
